{"text_id":27391,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," explored"," the"," potential"," of"," multiple"," antenna"," secure"," broadcast"," as"," a"," solution"," to"," the"," increasingly"," pressing"," issue"," of"," wireless"," security","."," The"," proliferation"," of"," wireless"," networks"," has"," led"," to"," an"," exponential"," increase"," in"," the"," number"," of"," devices"," connected"," to"," the"," internet","."," This"," growth"," has"," led"," to"," an"," increase"," in"," the"," likelihood"," of"," malicious"," actors"," gaining"," access"," to"," sensitive"," information",","," data"," breaches",","," and"," cyber","-","attacks","."," Our"," work"," aimed"," to"," explore"," the"," potential"," of"," deploying"," multiple"," antennas"," in"," the"," transmission"," of"," secure"," data"," over"," wireless"," networks","."," To"," accomplish"," this",","," we"," developed"," a"," novel"," approach"," that"," lever","ages"," Spatial"," Modulation"," (","SM",")"," technology"," to"," ensure"," secure"," and"," efficient"," communication"," across"," the"," network","."," Our"," method"," involved"," transmitting"," the"," data"," using"," multiple"," antennas",","," thereby"," reducing"," the"," risk"," of"," data"," loss",","," interception"," or"," eaves","dropping","."," The"," research"," yielded"," significant"," results",","," demonstrating"," the"," effectiveness"," of"," our"," proposed"," methodology"," in"," enhancing"," wireless"," security","."," In"," addition",","," the"," study"," presented"," a"," novel"," approach"," to"," wireless"," communication"," that"," could"," be"," useful"," across"," a"," variety"," of"," technological"," domains","."," Overall",","," our"," study"," showcased"," the"," potential"," of"," multiple"," antenna"," secure"," broadcast"," over"," wireless"," networks"," as"," a"," reliable"," and"," secure"," solution"," to"," modern"," wireless"," security"," challenges","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model